certified registered nurse practitioner or certified nurse
SB110 INTRODUCED
113 midwife in lieu of a physician pursuant to this section shall
114 be accepted as valid and lawful by the organization or entity
115 requesting a physician's signature."
116 Section 2. (a) For purposes of this section, an
117 athletic association has the same meaning as provided in
118 Section 16-1-52.1, Code of Alabama 1975.
119 (b) A public K-12 school may not be a member of an
120 athletic association that refuses to accept physical
121 examination forms to verify eligibility for students to
122 participate in K-12 school athletic activities which are
123 endorsed by a certified registered nurse practitioner or
124 certified nurse midwife in compliance with Section 34-21-93.1,
125 Code of Alabama 1975.
126 Section 3. This act shall become effective on October
127 1, 2026.
